title: Beginning LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3
description:
English | ISBN: 1430264365 | 2014 | 300 pages | PDF | 24 MB 

Beginning LEGO MINDSTORMS EV3 shows you how to create new fun and fantastic creations with the new EV3 programmable brick along with other new EV3 pieces and features. 

Youll learn the language of the EV3 brick, and then go on to create a variety of programmable vehicles using MINDSTORMS and Technic parts.
